<section class="card help"><h2>Quick start</h2><p>Register a land plot from Land Records, attach documents from Documents, then log any ownership change from Transactions.</p><h2>Transaction approval</h2><p>Officers create pending transactions. Admins review each transaction detail page and approve or reject it. Approval closes the previous current ownership and opens a new current ownership record.</p><h2>Document uploads</h2><p>Accepted files are PDF, JPG, PNG, and DOCX. Maximum size is 10MB per file.</p><h2>Roles</h2><p>Superadmins manage users and all records. Admins approve transactions and view audit logs. Officers register plots and transactions. Viewers read records and reports.</p><h2>Support</h2><p>Contact the CLMIS system administrator for account, data correction, or deployment support.</p></section>
